                        <div class="title-area mb-35">
                            <span class="sub-title">WHAT IS IOTLINK CHAIN?</span>
                            <h4 class="sec-title" style="font-size: large;">We are a robust smart network that uses bitcoin technology and proof-of-stake v3.0.</h4>
                            <p>Using PoS technology we are able to have a fast network, our tokens have a low gas fee for sending, being more affordable than other projects that bring a large gas fee. Each transaction uses UTXO, which is present in BITCOIN, bringing much more security to our network. Our concern is a green world so we eliminate mining from our code and each user only needs a few coins for their wallet to generate new coins on the network, simple right?</p>
