                    <div class="title-area">
                        <h2 class="text-white">SPECS IOTLINK CHAIN</h2>
                    </div>
                    <div class="text-area" style="color:white;">
We are a network that aims to improve the performance of bitcoin using its base code and implementing new features within it, including:<br><br>

POS3.0 - for an acceleration in the spacing in each block and bringing income to the holders of our coins.<br><br>

UTXO - Bitcoin payment system. UTXO is an acronym for Unspent Transaction Outputs. Unlike Ethereum's 'Account Balance Model', there is no account and balance, it verifies currency by examining the validity of a transaction through 'Unused Output'.<br><br>

ILC tokens (There cannot be tokens with the same name as the main network, since we are the main network and therefore a token).<br><br>

Minimum Fees - 0.0001ILC transaction depending on network congestion, fees will always be sent to the node that generated the block along with the PoS reward.<br><br>
Name: IoT Link Chain<br>

Ticker: ILC<br>

Premine:  20 000 000 ILC<br>

Proof Of Stake 3.0 enabled<br>

Stake reward: Fixed in 100 ILC  <br>

Tokenization enabled<br>

Fee issue new tokens: 2500 ILC<br>

Supply Token max: 100 000 000 000<br>

Governance enabled<br>

Fee transaction min: 0.0001 ILC<br>

Decimals: 8<br><br>
